title: The Maplin Electronic Circuits Handbook information, data
description: The Maplin Electronic Circuits Handbook information, data, explanations, and formulae for designing, constructing, and testing electronic circuits http://www.techbuzon.com/2017/03/electronic-devices-and-circuit.html Written for Maplin Electronics, purveyor of electronic components to enthusiasts and professionals. Provides background information, data, explanations, and formulae for designing, constructing, and testing electronic circuits. Also describes specific circuits for a wide range of tasks, designed to be the cheapest and easiest method. All components conveniently are identified by the Maplin part number. No bibliography. First published in 1988 as Electronic Circuits Handbook: Design, Testing and Construction . Annotation copyright Book News, Inc. Portland, Or
